MESSAGE.value: Support references across roots inside the same model, to enable refs from parser to lexer, when LexerRules are in different files. Expand visitor to support ebnfBlocks.
Support NotSet e.g., ~[\n\r]
Improve the visitor some more. Still missing a few bits to support the grammar of the R language.
Fix parsing of block. Was incorrectly returning empty alternatives.
Make grammars with no rules valid.
Paste R grammar. Almost there. Need to support range of characters to finish.
Draft tomps mapping configuration.
Preliminary support for tokens. Note that we now parse the grammar, rather than just the rules.
Fully support tokens. Now determine whether to paste rules or full grammar depending on the presence of "lexer grammar" or "parser grammar" in the text being pasted.
Support labeled parser elements.
Remove spuriour call to old Listener. Remove listerner implementation since it is no longer used.
Support resolving alternatives by id. This is useful when the language is imported again and we need to preserve the mapping with the previous version of the equivalent alternative.
Refactor mappers to support different kinds of sources (to be introduced).
Generate ruleref mappers.
Add Label now available on any ParserBlock. Change id() on Alternative to include names of tokens. Add a source for LabeledElements.
Support properties as destination of a mapping (no generation yet).
Support properties as destination of a mapping as well.
Add navigation on the source and destination of the mapper.
Add a new language for ANTLR4.5, to help as example and can populate from the grammar.
Improve generator.
Improve generator. Add ANTRL45 as language target for ANTRL grammar.

Add intention to label all the alternatives of a rule. Handle generation for labeled alternatives (needs testing). Add create concepts and labels intention (on concept mapper and in alternative mapper).

Add intention to label all the alternatives of a rule. Handle generation for labeled alternatives (needs testing). Add create concepts and labels intention (on concept mapper and in alternative mapper). Add concepts for elements of the metar.R language. Some concepts have incorrect names, but this will be changed with refactoring in the future (this language currently does not compile).
Redo R language, starting from prog and expr only.
Fix generation for lists of contexts.

option.value: Fix generation for lists of contexts.
